Package: fontconfig2
Version: 2.2.1
Revision: 1
Source: http://pdx.freedesktop.org/software/fontconfig/releases/fontconfig-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: a6a856606809b9ebfcc37a6380dcd6df
Patch: %n.patch
BuildDepends: freetype2 | freetype2-hinting, expat, x11-dev
Depends: %N-shlibs (>= %v-%r)
ConfigureParams: --prefix=%p/lib/%n --sysconfdir=/private/etc --bindir=%p/bin
InstallScript: <<
 make -j1 install DESTDIR=%d
 mkdir -p %i/share/doc
 mv %i/lib/%n/share/doc/* %i/share/doc/
 rm -rf %i/lib/%n/share
 rm -rf %d/private
<<
DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING ChangeLog INSTALL NEWS README
SplitOff: <<
  Package: %N-shlibs
  Depends: freetype2-shlibs | freetype2-hinting-shlibs, expat-shlibs, x11
  Files: lib/%N/lib/libfontconfig.*.dylib
  Shlibs: %p/lib/%N/lib/libfontconfig.1.dylib 2.0.0 (%n >= 2.2.0-1)
  Description: Shared libraries for fontconfig
<<
License: OSI-Approved
Description: Font configuration and control
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <ranger@befunk.com>
Homepage: http://freedesktop.org/software/fontconfig/
DescPackaging: <<
This package should not be linked against unless absolutely
necessary.  If you must link against it, you need to set
some variables.

  CPPFLAGS:        add -I%p/lib/fontconfig2/include
  CFLAGS:          you might need the same as CPPFLAGS
  LDFLAGS/LIBS:    add -L%p/lib/fontconfig2/lib
  PKG_CONFIG_PATH: add %p/lib/fontconfig2/lib/pkgconfig
<<
